CSS Notes

<style> </style> : Anything inside this tag is CSS

CSS Rule
1. selector with {}, can have multiple property: value;
selector {
    property: value;
    property2: value;
}

Change selector{} to any tag:
h1{
color: red;
}

body{
background:  //changes color of background
}

font-family: [font type];

button{
  background:
  border: //changes border, can set to none
  border-radius: 25px; //set border with rounded edges
}
